[11/06/2017 02:12:35] <font color="#00ff00">(JADEA)</font>
[11/06/2017 02:12:42] <font color="#00ff00">(JADEA)</font>
[11/06/2017 02:12:47] <font color="#00ff00">(GRITA)</font>
[11/06/2017 02:13:07] <font color="#00ff00">(JADEA)</font>
